THREAD: I‚Äôve been a consultant cancer specialist for 15yrs. Seasonal flu has NEVER seriously impacted my clinical practice.
On the contrary #COVID19 has had a dramatic impact, so all those on social media calling to end lockdown need to understand the seriousness of this pandemic

For starters, I‚Äôve been assigned to the #COVID19 wards rota. Somewhat scary for a non-acute physician, but actually a privilege to be able to help the dedicated teams on the frontline.
Meanwhile, the cancer service must continue.....

Interestingly, I‚Äôm actuality giving more lung cancer radiotherapy than ever before, because the surgeons are operating much less due to #COVID19 risks, and we can use stereotactic radiotherapy to treat early stage lung cancer as a very good alternative to surgery.

In summary, social commentators who want to reopen the country on the basis that they think the #COVID19 pandemic is no worse seasonal flu, are dangerously wrong. Stay at home as per advice. It‚Äôs tough, but we need to hang in there. The public have been amazing so far. Keep it up
